<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">合并扩整法，计算连乘法时，如果遇到两个因数相乘可得到整十、整百、整千......的数，可根据乘法运算的交换律、结合律及运算性质，先合并扩整，然后再相乘。</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">25×5×125×4×8=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 25×5×125×4×8</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=(25×4)×(125×8)×5</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=100×1000×5</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=500000</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>